The Queen is a former TV journalist with a wardrobe that gives the Duchess of Cambridge a run for her money. And today she didn't disappoint, wearing a smart but chic outfit befitting the serious occasion.

She wore a stone coloured tweed suit with a lace overlay and a waist clinching belt teamed with colour coordinating heels.

Meanwhile, her husband was in military dress as he gave a speech to the assembled troops.

