She added some bling to her minimalistic outfit with the help of a pair of dazzling diamond earrings and wore her hair in its trademark sleek style.

The exhibition, which runs until October, marks the IV Centenary of the death of artist El Greco.

It will exhibit 26 pieces of his work and aims to highlight the Cretan painter's work in the nineteenth and twentieth centuries.

